        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Job 20:23",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " (cf. below ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Psalm 78:64",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). מלאכי רעים are not wicked angels, against which view Hengstenberg refers to the scriptural thesis of Jacobus Ode in his work De Angelis, Deum ad puniendos malos homines mittere bonos angelos et ad castigandos pios usurpare malos, but angels that bring misfortune. The mode of construction belongs to the chapter of the genitival subordination of the adjective to the substantive, like אשׁת רע, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Proverbs 6:24",
        "children": []
